<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Abhiruchii Restaurant | Best Biryani in Chirala</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
* {margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box;}
body {font-family:'Poppins', sans-serif; background:#FFF8E7; color:#333;}

.hero {
height:100vh;
background:linear-gradient(rgba(139,0,0,0.7), rgba(139,0,0,0.7)),
url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604908177522-432c26f0d48e');
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
}

.hero h1 {font-size:3rem; margin-bottom:20px;}
.hero p {font-size:1.2rem; margin-bottom:30px;}

.btn {
background:#FF6B00;
color:white;
padding:12px 30px;
border:none;
border-radius:30px;
font-size:1rem;
cursor:pointer;
transition:0.3s;
text-decoration:none;
}

.btn:hover {background:#e65c00;}

.section {padding:80px 20px; text-align:center;}

.cards {
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
justify-content:center;
gap:30px;
margin-top:40px;
}

.card {
background:white;
padding:25px;
border-radius:15px;
width:280px;
box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
transform:translateY(-10px);
}

.card h3 {margin-bottom:15px;}

.cta {
background:#8B0000;
color:white;
padding:60px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

footer {
background:#1A1A1A;
color:white;
padding:30px;
text-align:center;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hero">
<h1>Authentic Andhra Flavours</h1>
<p>Spicy. Fresh. Unforgettable.</p>
<a href="tel:08594239907" class="btn">Call & Reserve Now</a>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>Our Signature Dishes</h2>

<div class="cards">
<div class="card">
<h3>Chicken Biryani</h3>
<p>Bold spices and rich aroma that define Andhra taste.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Mutton Biryani</h3>
<p>Slow-cooked perfection with authentic flavors.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>Chilli Chicken</h3>
<p>The perfect spicy starter loved by everyone.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
<p>✔ 7,000+ Happy Customers</p>
<p>✔ Budget Friendly (₹200–400)</p>
<p>✔ Prime Location in Chirala</p>
<p>✔ Fast Service</p>
</div>

<div class="cta">
<h2>Ready to Experience Real Andhra Spice?</h2>
<br>
<a href="tel:08594239907" class="btn">Book Your Table</a>
</div>

<footer>
<p>Abhiruchii Restaurant | Chirala</p>
<p>Open Till 10:30 PM</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
